touch frontend_app.py

--------------------------------------------
# .gitignore -->
__pycache__/ â†’ ignores the whole folder where Python stores compiled files

*.pyc â†’ ignores compiled bytecode files directly

.env â†’ hides your secrets (PIN, email passwords)

logs/ â†’ hides logs like tracker.log

--------------------------------------------


# ðŸ“Š Employee Tracker - FastAPI + Streamlit + Docker

> A real-world Employee Management System built with **Python**, **FastAPI**, **Streamlit**, and **Docker**, supporting attendance, performance tracking, and secure PIN-based access.

---

## ðŸ“ Folder Structure Overview

```
employee-tracker/
â”œâ”€â”€ app/
